---

<div class="relative overflow-hidden bg-white/70 pt-36 pb-20">
	<div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-full -z-10 opacity-10">
		<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-violetaIA/30 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
		<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-verdeEsm/20 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
	</div>

	<main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
		<section class="grid items-center gap-12 md:grid-cols-2">
			<div class="text-left">
				<span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 mb-6 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 rounded-full">
					Smart Auditing â€¢ Sustainable Growth
				</span>
				<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-azulCorp leading-[1.1] mb-8">
					Auditoria inteligente para un futuro
					<span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-violetaIA via-azulCorp to-verdeEsm animate-pulse">
						sostenible
					</span>
				</h1>
				<p class="max-w-2xl text-lg text-slate-600 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
					Transformamos la certeza financiera mediante la integracion de Inteligencia Artificial y estandares globales de sostenibilidad[cite: 34].
				</p>
				<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
					<a
						href="#servicios"
						class="px-8 py-4 bg-azulCorp text-white rounded-xl font-semibold hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-violetaIA/20 transition-all"
					>
						Explorar Servicios
					</a>
					<a
						href="/nosotros"
						class="px-8 py-4 border border-slate-200 text-azulCorp rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-slate-50 transition-all"
					>
						Nuestra Filosofia
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="relative">
				<div class="absolute -inset-4 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-violetaIA/15 via-transparent to-verdeEsm/15 blur-2xl"></div>
				<div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2.5rem] border border-slate-200 bg-white/80 p-6 shadow-2xl">
					<div class="aspect-[4/3] w-full rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-200 via-white to-slate-100"></div>
					<div class="mt-6 flex items-center justify-between text-xs text-slate-500">
						<span>Equipo + datos en tiempo real</span>
						<span>Naturaleza + IA</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="servicios" class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
			<div class="p-8 bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-3xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all group">
				<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-violetaIA/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
					<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-violetaIA" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path
							stroke-linecap="round"
							stroke-linejoin="round"
							stroke-width="2"
							d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.989-2.386l-.548-.547z"
						></path>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Smart Audit</h3>
				<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
					Analisis integral de datos mediante Machine Learning para erradicar el error humano[cite: 133].
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="p-8 bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-3xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all group">
				<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-verdeEsm/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
					<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-verdeEsm" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path
							stroke-linecap="round"
							stroke-linejoin="round"
							stroke-width="2"
							d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"
						></path>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">ESG Strategy</h3>
				<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
					Convertimos la responsabilidad ambiental en un activo estrategico y valor financiero[cite: 143].
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="p-8 bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-3xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all group">
				<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-azulCorp/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
					<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-azulCorp" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path
							stroke-linecap="round"
							stroke-linejoin="round"
							stroke-width="2"
							d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5z"
						></path>
						<path
							stroke-linecap="round"
							stroke-linejoin="round"
							stroke-width="2"
							d="M12 14l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14z"
						></path>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Executive Academy</h3>
				<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
					Executive Knowledge Hub para dominar la IA aplicada a la alta direccion financiera[cite: 152].
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</div>
